snippet.title: TRY TO RESIST LAUGHING - Funniest ANIMAL fails & moments
snippet.description:
Animals are so funny that you just can't resist laughing! They will make you happy no matter what! Just look how all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, horses, monkeys, goats,... behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things, feel guilty... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
